  "title": "Construction Carpenter",
  "description": "<p>Key Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Measure, cut, and shape wood, plastic, and other materials using hand and power tools</li>\n  <li>Read and interpret blueprints, drawings, and sketches to determine specifications and calculate requirements</li>\n  <li>Inspect, Install and Repair structures and fixtures</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with general contractors, electricians, plumbers, and other construction professionals</li>\n  <li>Ensure all work complies with local building codes and safety regulations.</li>\n  <li>Maintain a clean and safe working environment.</li>\n  <li>Estimate material requirements and manage inventory on-site.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Proficiency with tools and construction materials</li>\n  <li>Proven carpentry experience in construction</li>\n  <li>Able to communicate with others and read technical documents and drawings</li>\n  <li>Physically fit and have good endurance</li>\n  <li>Must have valid and relevant licence and certificates</li>\n  <li>Required to work on site in shifts</li>\n</ul>",
